title: Deluge T1 T2 Return (2011) (Sosich) cbr
description:
Global warming, climate disturbance or simple anger of the Gods, no one knows anymore nor do they remember. But the flood happened and humanity split between those who went into the stars and those who sunk into the seas. That was an eternity ago. Today, Captain Jason, a nomad of the seas, is the only witness to the emergency splash-down of a gigantic human space shuttle.

enjoy
